00:13:15.350 --> 00:13:16.350
Excellent.

00:13:16.350 --> 00:13:17.350
We are.

00:13:17.350 --> 00:13:18.350
Yeah.

00:13:18.350 --> 00:13:19.350
Vanessa: We are.

00:13:19.350 --> 00:13:21.630
Vanessa: We're talking you through this lesson.

