quick?

00:18:24.779 --> 00:18:28.750
Dan: It's not really, really mind-blowing,
but you say it.

00:18:28.750 --> 00:18:30.039
Vanessa: Exaggeration maybe.

00:18:30.039 --> 00:18:32.320
