use that to just really let people know it

00:19:00.710 --> 00:19:01.710
was really cool.

00:19:01.710 --> 00:19:02.710
It was amazing.

00:19:02.710 --> 00:19:03.710
Vanessa: Yeah.

00:19:03.710 --> 00:19:04.710
